{
  "stem": "71.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we heard-- we heard in Auschwitz that Mengele who's the doctor that made the separations, that he separates twins and sisters because one should not keep up the spirit of the other.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you don't have anybody, he said, you probably will die faster.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but some-- we were told that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- So when we found this out and we were transferred later to a barrack where there were younger children, and it was close to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my both sisters went out, and there was a garbage can with potato peels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they got some potato peels and somebody noticed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they called them, they told them, and the road was of stones, very pointy stones that, you know, your feet when you had no shoes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they called [INAUDIBLE], who was the highest official of Auschwitz, and she made them kneel down on these stones and then she took both heads of my sisters and just knocked them both together in-- in-- in a force and she told them to run back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wouldn't-- she wouldn't-- they would not-- she wouldn't give them even the peels anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were just-- they came, they-- they could not see straight because, you know, sparks were in front of their eyes from that impact of both heads.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later we found-- we found out that we are going on a transport and they took us out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the nights were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were laying there, and if you had to go to release yourself, there was a pail outside in the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were electric wires in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were a few times, and this is not making up stories.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
